@node ryde "Ryder Cup Golf"

                Ryder Cup             Ocean             £30

Ryder Cup Golf is one of those games which I cannot help feeling
indifferent about.  It has nice graphics, bad sound effects, good fast
screen updates and difficult controls.  The bad cancels out the good,
and you are left with a pretty standard Golf sim.  It's better than Nick
